# OneWater Pakistan — Frontend Environment Variables
# All VITE_SUPABASE_* variables have been removed.
# The frontend now communicates exclusively through the Node.js/Express backend.

# In development: leave VITE_API_URL empty — Vite proxy routes /api/* → http://localhost:5000 (see vite.config.ts)
# In production (Vercel): set VITE_API_URL=https://one-water-backend.onrender.com in the Vercel dashboard env vars
VITE_API_URL=""
